---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Careers"
  description="Join the Alved Services team. We are hiring Direct Support Professionals who care about making a real difference in the lives of adults with intellectual and developmental disabilities."
>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero" aria-label="Careers at Alved Services">
    <div class="wrap page-hero-inner reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Careers</span>
      <h1>Make a difference every day.</h1>
      <p class="lead">At Alved Services, our Direct Support Professionals are the heart of everything we do. If you care about helping adults with intellectual and developmental disabilities live meaningful, independent lives, we want to hear from you.</p>
      <a href="#apply" class="btn btn-gold">Press here to Apply Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY WORK HERE -->
  <section class="why-section" aria-labelledby="why-heading">
    <div class="why-bg-shape" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why Alved Services</span>
        <h2 id="why-heading">A team that shows up for each other</h2>
        <p>We believe the people who support our individuals deserve the same care, respect, and dignity we provide to the adults we serve.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid" role="list">
        <article class="why-card reveal" role="listitem">
          <div class="why-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌟</div>
          <h3>Meaningful Work</h3>
          <p>Every day you show up, you make a real difference in someone's life. This work matters, and we never lose sight of that.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="why-card reveal reveal--delay" role="listitem">
          <div class="why-icon" aria-hidden="true">📚</div>
          <h3>Training & Support</h3>
          <p>We provide thorough onboarding, ongoing training, and the support you need to do your job well and grow in your role.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="why-card reveal reveal--delay-2" role="listitem">
          <div class="why-icon" aria-hidden="true">🤝</div>
          <h3>Respectful Environment</h3>
          <p>We treat our team members the same way we treat the individuals we serve, with dignity, respect, and genuine care.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="why-card reveal reveal--delay-3" role="listitem">
          <div class="why-icon" aria-hidden="true">📅</div>
          <h3>Flexible Scheduling</h3>
          <p>We offer both full-time and part-time positions with scheduling that works around your life, not just ours.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EDITORIAL PHOTOS -->
  <section class="editorial-section" aria-labelledby="editorial-heading">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Life at Alved Services</span>
        <h2 id="editorial-heading">What the work actually looks like</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="editorial-row reveal">
        <div class="editorial-img">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576765608535-5f04d1e3f289?w=800&q=80" alt="A Direct Support Professional working alongside an adult individual in the community" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-text">
          <span class="ed-tag">Direct Support</span>
          <h3>You go where the individual goes</h3>
          <p>As a DSP, your work happens at home, in the community, at work sites, and during recreational activities. No two days look the same, and that is part of what makes it rewarding.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="editorial-row editorial-row--flip reveal">
        <div class="editorial-text">
          <span class="ed-tag">Real Impact</span>
          <h3>Small moments, big difference</h3>
          <p>Whether it is helping someone learn a new skill, supporting a community outing, or just being a consistent and caring presence, the work you do shapes lives in real, lasting ways.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-img">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1491438590914-bc09fcaaf77a?w=800&q=80" alt="Support staff and adults participating in a community activity together" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OPEN POSITIONS -->
  <section class="positions-section" aria-labelledby="positions-heading">
    <div class="positions-bg-shape" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Open Positions</span>
        <h2 id="positions-heading">We are currently hiring</h2>
        <p>All positions work directly with adults with intellectual and developmental disabilities across Marion County.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="positions-list reveal" role="list">

        <!-- DSP ACCORDION -->
        <article class="position-card" role="listitem">
          <div class="position-header" id="dsp-header">
            <div class="position-info">
              <h3>Direct Support Professional (DSP)</h3>
              <div class="position-meta">
                <span class="meta-tag">Full-time</span>
                <span class="meta-tag">Part-time</span>
                <span class="meta-tag">Marion County</span>
                <span class="meta-tag">Non-Exempt Hourly</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <button class="expand-btn" id="dspToggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="dspDetails">
              <span class="expand-text">Press here to View Position</span>
              <span class="expand-icon" aria-hidden="true">＋</span>
            </button>
          </div>

          <div class="position-details" id="dspDetails" hidden>
            <div class="job-description">

              <div class="jd-section">
                <h4>About This Role</h4>
                <p>The Direct Support Professional (DSP) reports to the Supervisor at Alved Services, ensuring quality support by developing and monitoring the implementation of individualized care plans. DSPs are responsible for supporting individuals as prescribed within their Individual Support Plans (ISP), providing quality support and care, and increasing quality of life in the direction of each individual's choice.</p>
                <p>Consistent attendance is required for this position.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="jd-section">
                <h4>What You Will Do</h4>
                <p>As a DSP, you will support adults with intellectual and developmental disabilities in the following areas:</p>
                <div class="jd-grid">
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Personal Care</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Assisting with personal hygiene, grooming, bathing, toileting, oral care, shaving, and dressing</li>
                      <li>Meal planning, preparation, and assistance with dining</li>
                      <li>Medication assistance as prescribed</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Home & Safety</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Maintaining a clean, safe, and well-kept living environment</li>
                      <li>Testing smoke and CO2 alarms, maintaining safe water temperatures</li>
                      <li>Monitoring health-related issues and responding to emergencies</li>
                      <li>Providing quality care in the individual's home as needed</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Community & Transportation</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Providing transportation for social, medical, and general needs</li>
                      <li>Supporting community access, employment, and recreational activities</li>
                      <li>Assisting individuals to engage in activities of their choice</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Independence & Advocacy</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Promoting independence through prompts, not doing tasks for the individual</li>
                      <li>Supporting communication and self-advocacy</li>
                      <li>Inspiring dignity and respect in every interaction at all times</li>
                      <li>Encouraging and supporting individuals to meet their personal outcome goals</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Documentation</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Maintaining accurate and timely records and documentation</li>
                      <li>Clear and professional written and verbal communication</li>
                      <li>Maintaining professional relationships with Alved Services staff and management</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Health Monitoring</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Monitoring health conditions such as dysphagia, seizures, and diabetes</li>
                      <li>Assisting with medical appointments as needed</li>
                      <li>Understanding and responding appropriately to behavioral support needs</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="jd-section">
                <h4>Qualifications</h4>
                <div class="jd-grid">
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Education & Certifications</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>High School Diploma or GED required</li>
                      <li>Current CPR Certification</li>
                      <li>Current First Aid Certification</li>
                      <li>CNA License preferred, not required</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Requirements</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Must be at least 18 years old</li>
                      <li>Must be fluent in English, read and write</li>
                      <li>Legally authorized to work in the United States</li>
                      <li>Valid Driver's License or State ID with liability insurance</li>
                      <li>Acceptable criminal background and abuse/neglect registry check</li>
                      <li>Indiana DSP Registry enrollment (required as of January 1, 2026)</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Physical Requirements</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Ability to bend, stoop, sit, stand, and reach</li>
                      <li>Ability to lift and assist individuals up to 75 pounds</li>
                      <li>Ability to stand for extended periods</li>
                      <li>Ability to respond effectively in emergency situations</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="jd-group">
                    <h5>Skills & Qualities</h5>
                    <ul role="list">
                      <li>Compassion and empathy for the individuals you support</li>
                      <li>Strong communication skills, written and verbal</li>
                      <li>Ability to work independently with sound judgment</li>
                      <li>Ability to follow individualized care plans accurately</li>
                      <li>Computer experience with Word, Excel, and related software</li>
                      <li>Patience, reliability, and consistent attendance</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="jd-eeo">
                <h4>Equal Opportunity Employer</h4>
                <p>Alved Services, LLC is an equal opportunity employer and does not discriminate against qualified applicants or employees on account of race, color, sex (including pregnancy and related conditions), age, national origin, marital status, physical or mental disability, or any other protected category under federal or state laws and local ordinances. Alved Services prohibits any form of workplace harassment, misconduct, or abuse.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="jd-apply">
                <a href="#apply" class="btn btn-gold">Press here to Apply for This Position</a>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPLICATION FORM -->
  <section class="apply-section" aria-labelledby="apply-heading" id="apply">
    <div class="apply-bg-shape" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Apply</span>
        <h2 id="apply-heading">Employment Application</h2>
        <p>Complete all fields below. Applications are actively considered for 3 months after submission. If you need help completing this application, please call us at <a href="tel:+17654918616">(765) 491-8616</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="app-form reveal" role="form" aria-label="Employment application form">

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>Personal Information</legend>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="field">
              <label for="fname">First Name <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" autocomplete="given-name" required />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label for="lname">Last Name <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="lname" name="lname" autocomplete="family-name" required />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label for="email">Email Address <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label for="phone">Phone Number <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" required />
            </div>
            <div class="field field--full">
              <label for="address">Street Address</label>
              <input type="text" id="address" name="address" autocomplete="street-address" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>Position</legend>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="field">
              <label for="position">Position Applying For <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <select id="position" name="position" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select a position</option>
                <option>Direct Support Professional (DSP)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label for="type">Employment Type <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <select id="type" name="type" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select type</option>
                <option>Full-time</option>
                <option>Part-time</option>
                <option>Either</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="field field--full">
              <label for="availability">Availability <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="availability" name="availability" placeholder="e.g. Weekdays, evenings, weekends" required />
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>Background & Experience</legend>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="field field--full">
              <label for="education">Highest Level of Education <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <select id="education" name="education" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select</option>
                <option>High School Diploma / GED</option>
                <option>Some College</option>
                <option>Associate's Degree</option>
                <option>Bachelor's Degree</option>
                <option>Graduate Degree</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="field field--full">
              <label for="experience">Relevant Experience</label>
              <textarea id="experience" name="experience" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us about any experience supporting individuals with I/DD, caregiving, or related work."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="field field--full">
              <label for="why">Why do you want to work at Alved Services?</label>
              <textarea id="why" name="why" rows="3" placeholder="Share what draws you to this kind of work."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="field field--full">
              <label for="convicted">Have you ever been convicted of a crime? <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
              <select id="convicted" name="convicted" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select</option>
                <option value="no">No</option>
                <option value="yes">Yes</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="field field--full" id="convictedDetails" style="display:none;">
              <label for="convictedExplain">If yes, please explain</label>
              <textarea id="convictedExplain" name="convictedExplain" rows="3" placeholder="A conviction does not automatically disqualify you. Please provide details."></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>Eligibility & Consent</legend>
          <div class="consent-list">
            <div class="consent-item">
              <input type="checkbox" id="age18" name="age18" required />
              <label for="age18">I confirm that I am 18 years of age or older. <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            </div>
            <div class="consent-item">
              <input type="checkbox" id="english" name="english" required />
              <label for="english">I confirm that I am fluent in English and able to read and write in English. <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            </div>
            <div class="consent-item">
              <input type="checkbox" id="legalWork" name="legalWork" required />
              <label for="legalWork">I confirm that I am legally authorized to work in the United States. <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            </div>
            <div class="consent-item">
              <input type="checkbox" id="bgcheck" name="bgcheck" required />
              <label for="bgcheck">I consent to a criminal history background check and an abuse/neglect registry check as required for this position. <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            </div>
            <div class="consent-item">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dspregistry" name="dspregistry" required />
              <label for="dspregistry">I understand that Indiana requires Direct Support Professionals to be registered with the state DSP Registry before providing direct support services, effective January 1, 2026. <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            </div>
            <div class="consent-item">
              <input type="checkbox" id="eeo" name="eeo" required />
              <label for="eeo">I certify that all information in this application is accurate to the best of my knowledge, and I acknowledge Alved Services is an equal opportunity employer. <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span></label>
            </div>
            <div class="consent-item consent-item--optional">
              <input type="checkbox" id="hadHelp" name="hadHelp" />
              <label for="hadHelp">I had assistance completing this application. <span class="optional-label">(Optional)</span></label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="form-note">This application will be actively considered for 3 months after submission. To be considered after that period, a new application must be submitted.</p>
        </fieldset>

        <div class="form-submit">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold btn-submit">Press here to Submit Application</button>
          <p class="form-note">Fields marked <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span> are required.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="careers-cta" aria-label="Questions about careers">
    <div class="cta-bg-shape" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="wrap careers-cta-inner reveal">
      <h2>Questions before you apply?</h2>
      <p>We are happy to answer any questions about working at Alved Services before you submit your application.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost-light">Press here to Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { position: relative; padding: 100px 0 90px; overflow: hidden; }
  .page-hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?w=1600&q=80') center/cover no-repeat; z-index: 0; }
  .page-hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,42,69,0.93) 0%, rgba(31,58,95,0.82) 60%, rgba(31,58,95,0.65) 100%); z-index: 1; }
  .page-hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 700px; }
  .page-hero .eyebrow { color: var(--gold-soft); }
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--white); font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .page-hero .lead { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 580px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .btn-gold { background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy-deep); font-weight: 700; }
  .btn-gold:hover { background: #a07820; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .why-section { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .why-bg-shape { position: absolute; top: -100px; right: -100px; width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(184,144,44,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
  .section-head { max-width: 580px; margin-bottom: 44px; }
  .section-head h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .section-head p { color: var(--ink-soft); }
  .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 18px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .why-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 22px; border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold-soft); transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease; }
  .why-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 30px -10px rgba(31,58,95,0.15); border-bottom-color: var(--gold); }
  .why-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .why-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .why-card p { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }

  .editorial-section { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; background: var(--bg-alt); }
  .editorial-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 50px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .editorial-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .editorial-img { border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; }
  .editorial-img img { width: 100%; height: 320px; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .ed-tag { display: inline-block; background: var(--gold-soft); color: var(--navy-deep); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .editorial-text h3 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .editorial-text p { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  .positions-section { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .positions-bg-shape { position: absolute; bottom: -80px; left: -80px; width: 400px; height: 400px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(31,58,95,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
  .positions-list { display: grid; gap: 14px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .position-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; }
  .position-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 20px; padding: 24px 28px; cursor: pointer; }
  .position-info h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .position-meta { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .meta-tag { background: var(--bg-alt); color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .expand-btn { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); border: none; border-radius: 30px; padding: 10px 18px; font-size: 0.88rem; font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; flex-shrink: 0; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .expand-btn:hover { background: var(--navy-deep); }
  .expand-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
  .expand-btn[aria-expanded="true"] .expand-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .expand-btn[aria-expanded="true"] .expand-text { display: none; }
  .expand-btn[aria-expanded="true"]::before { content: 'Close Position'; }

  .position-details { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .job-description { padding: 36px 28px; }
  .jd-section { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .jd-section h4 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold-soft); }
  .jd-section p { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.93rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .jd-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .jd-group h5 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .jd-group ul { list-style: none; display: grid; gap: 6px; }
  .jd-group li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ink-soft); display: flex; gap: 8px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .jd-group li::before { content: "✓"; color: var(--sage); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .jd-eeo { background: var(--bg-alt); border-radius: 10px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .jd-eeo h4 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .jd-eeo p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }
  .jd-apply { text-align: center; padding-top: 10px; }

  .apply-section { background: var(--bg-alt); padding: var(--section-pad) 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .apply-bg-shape { position: absolute; top: -100px; right: -100px; width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(184,144,44,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
